-- Monte dei Paschi appoints Fintech, BTG Pactual board members
-- 
-- Thu Oct 09, 2014 01:44PM EDT
-- None



MILAN, Oct 9 (Reuters) - Monte dei Paschi di Siena (MPS) on Thursday said it had appointed two representatives from the bank's key investors, Fintech Advisory and BTG Pactual, to its management board.

Billionaire Mexican investor David Martinez will represent U.S.-based Fintech Advisory's interest in the Tuscan lender, while Roberto Isolani will sit for the Brazillian bank.